{"id": "1360259453416509450", "channel_id": "1360259298139308072", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "2.2.0.2 Maintenance Notice\n \nDear Keeper,\n    Mythag University will undergo facility maintenance on April 14 from 08:00 to 11:00 (UTC+8).\n    After maintenance, you will need to log in again and update resources. Supplies will be sent via mail. For any questions, please contact the campus customer service center. Thank you for your understanding and support!\n\n【Supplies】\nMaintenance Compensation:  Silver*200, Pure Core*5\n\n【Claim Conditions】\nClaim period ends on April 28, 2025, at 09:00. Please remember to collect your supplies from the mailbox in time.\n\n【Update Content】\n1. Battle\n【Awaker: Clementine】\n● Talent \"Swarm Sense\": At the start of the Ultra turn, for every removal of all enemies' 1 layer of \"Fear Fixation,\" increase the Aliemus gained by other Awakers from 1 to 2.\n● Enlighten 2 \"Soul Healing Journey\": After each battle, increase Clementine's base damage by 25%.\n● Aliemus Burst \"Life Reconstruction Healing\": Now converts \"Mental Trauma\" or \"Fear Fixation\" before dealing damage.\n\n【Awaker: Tawil】\n● Fixed the issue where Tawil could incorrectly stack \"Empathy\" layers when using Clementine's command card \"Pain Extraction.\"\n\n【Awaker: Salvador】\n● Ultra Burst \"Rite of Creation\": Fixed the issue where after reaching the maximum number of \"Scarlet Furnace\" stacks, it could incorrectly reset in the next battle.\n● Gnosis Adaptation: Fixed the issue where selecting \"Sense\" in \"Ashen Ruins\" did not correctly increase max health.\n\n【Realm: Deep Sea】\n● Fixed the issue where Deep Sea Tentacle damage base value was incorrectly affected by \"Final Damage,\" \"Weakness,\" etc., causing multiple erroneous effects on actual damage.\n\n【Realm: Ultra】\n● Affix \"Transdistance\": When taken from Ultra space, the Arithmetica cost of the corresponding card is reduced by 1.\n\n【Posse: Special Treatment】", "timestamp": "2025-04-11T14:25:26.093000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1360259298139308072", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.2.0.2 停服維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
